      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues] Line 93: The script writes a fixed `/tmp/.qos_lab_ipfwd_saved` file and later trusts its contents as root. On shared systems this is vulnerable to symlink/clobbering and state injection. Use a private temp directory created with `mktemp -d`, restrict permissions, and clean it up, or store the previous value in memory for the lifetime of the command.",
